{"tid":770492,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"電動輪椅伯伯馬路逆線行　網民：嫌命長？","createTime":"2018-08-07T06:46:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-07T08:04:31.000Z","uid":39464,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"0da8dc1c2a12ed8853d930391898eba96670210c","tid":770492,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T06:46:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180807/photo/bkn-20180807131933858-0807_00822_001_01p.jpg?20180807142537\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180807%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180807131933858-0807_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20180807142537&h=f3ecda91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然電動輪椅為不少行動不便的長者帶來方便，不過部分人的「駕駛」態度，則隨時害人害己。日前有車Cam就拍得一名坐着電動輪椅的伯伯在馬路上「逆線行駛」，迎頭駛至的車輛閃避相讓，情況牙煙。 <br />\n<br />\n現場是將軍澳坑口，片段開始，一輛私家車行駛至一個彎位前，一名坐着電動輪椅的伯伯棄旁邊行人路不用，選擇在車來車往的馬路上逆線行駛。幸迎面而來的私家車司機及時發現，扭軚閃避，才未有發生意外。期間伯伯表現悠閒，似未察覺危險，繼續施施然向前駛。 <br />\n<br />\n不少網民狠批伯伯「嫌命長」，有人更諷刺謂：「好多人坐住部電動輪椅喺馬路及行人路兩邊走，有時行馬路，有燈位又上番行人路，真方便。」 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180807/bkn-20180807131933858-0807_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180807%2Fbkn-20180807131933858-0807_00822_001.html&d=gV%2FhBUUaK4F2E3PEbKxKdtr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=807cce60\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180807/bkn-20180807131933858-0807_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"9c48cef6445f38ad23d1d43d48c5193461f2a992","tid":770492,"uid":132587,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T06:49:39.000Z","msg":"香港果d電動輪椅呀叔真係當正自己渣緊f1<br />\n最鐘意係條路片黎片去<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c53a160f0d076180d7fff556f6460a3aab5d0dd0","tid":770492,"uid":70301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T06:51:02.000Z","msg":"將軍澳坑口？<br />\n厚德邨是咪咪喺嗰頭？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/n